TY  - JOUR
TI  - Schooling and the Farm Problem
AU  - Gisser, Micha
AB  - [This article is an econometric study of the relationship between the level of schooling in rural farm areas and income of farm workers. The following shows that more schooling in rural farm areas will accelerate the process of farm outmigration, thus relieving farmers of their poverty.]
